        "timestamp": "2019-04-11 13:43:40.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Please comment on the need to bump from v14 to v16 on this change\n\nI had updated pom.xml in babel to use the latest schema version for Dublin. Isn't it ok to use the same for this mS?\nThe way the code works is the artifacts generated use the latest version of the xsd schemas generated based on the version provided in pom.xml\n\nIn pom.xml, the jar version used is \n<aai-schema.group.id>org.onap.aai.schema-service</aai-schema.group.id>\n<aai-schema.version>1.0.2</aai-schema.version>\n\nThe script included in pom.xml get-latest-xsd-version.sh determines the version to use.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
